    net.opentsdb.query.expression  

    • Uses of ITimeSyncedIterator in net.opentsdb.query.expression

      Classes in net.opentsdb.query.expression that implement ITimeSyncedIterator 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  ExpressionIterator
      A iterator that applies an expression to the results of multiple sub queries.
      class  IntersectionIterator
      This class handles taking a set of queries and their results and iterates over each series in each set with time alignment after computing the intersection of all sets.
      class  TimeSyncedIterator
      Holds the results of a sub query (a single metric) and iterates over each resultant series in lock-step for expression evaluation.
      class  UnionIterator
      An iterator that computes the union of all series in the result sets.
